ddle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-promotes-multinational-force-to-secure-delivery-of-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018e-8aea-d49b-a3bf-feff09e80000</link><description>这支部队将依靠友好的阿拉伯国家的代表，保卫援助车队和美国正在加沙沿岸建设的港口</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 17:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-promotes-multinational-force-to-secure-delivery-of-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018e-8aea-d49b-a3bf-feff09e80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡最大的伎俩？欺骗全世界把他视为政治奇才</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-greatest-trick-fooling-the-world-into-seeing-him-as-a-political-wizard/0000018e-8a3d-d0d3-a98e-deff67f10000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡已经成为一个沮丧、垂头丧气和失败的领导人，他现在试图在人行道上在难以置信和愤怒的路人面前表演恶作剧</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 16:29:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-greatest-trick-fooling-the-world-into-seeing-him-as-a-political-wizard/0000018e-8a3d-d0d3-a98e-deff67f10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 175 天：以色列代表团前往多哈和开罗进行停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-175-israeli-delegations-to-depart-for-doha-cairo-for-truce-talks/0000018e-8af2-d9a4-a7bf-cefb0d120001</link><description>以色列国防军称，真主党火箭和导弹部队副指挥官被打死 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列将加大对真主党的攻击力度 ■ 以色列代表团前往多哈和开罗继续谈判 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在汗尤尼斯被火箭弹炸死，16 人受伤 ■ 第三个星期五耶路撒冷阿克萨清真寺的斋月祈祷结束，没有异常骚乱 ■ 战争结束 175 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 16:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-175-israeli-delegations-to-depart-for-doha-cairo-for-truce-talks/0000018e-8af2-d9a4-a7bf-cefb0d120001</guid></item><item><title>活动人士警告称，以色列警方计划加强在示威活动中的存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-plan-to-bolster-presence-at-demonstrations-warn-activists/0000018e-8a7b-d0d3-a98e-deff66e70000</link><description>警方正准备在本周六开始的抗议活动中增加警力，而活动人士则亲自收到特拉维夫地区指挥官的来信，呼吁他们停止活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 15:33:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-plan-to-bolster-presence-at-demonstrations-warn-activists/0000018e-8a7b-d0d3-a98e-deff66e70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙被俘以色列士兵的父母在会见内塔尼亚胡后：我们没有得到答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-captured-idf-soldiers-after-meeting-netanyahu-we-got-no-answers/0000018e-898d-d0d3-a98e-dfff82ed0000</link><description>一名被关押在加沙的以色列国防军士兵的父亲表示，总理“忙于度过当前的危机”，而不是确保他们的儿子安全返回。另一位家长表示，他们从内塔尼亚胡那里听到了同样的信息，就好像距离上次人质释放还没有过去 100 天一样。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 10:45:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-captured-idf-soldiers-after-meeting-netanyahu-we-got-no-answers/0000018e-898d-d0d3-a98e-dfff82ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列击毙黎巴嫩真主党最高指挥官 叙利亚空袭造成数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes-targeting-hezbollah-members-syrian-associates/0000018e-8933-d0d3-a98e-dfff4ced0000</link><description>以色列称，它杀死了黎巴嫩南部真主党火箭和导弹部队的副指挥官，而据报道，叙利亚阿勒颇附近的另一次袭击造成数十人伤亡，其中大部分是阿萨德政权部队</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 09:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes-targeting-hezbollah-members-syrian-associates/0000018e-8933-d0d3-a98e-dfff4ced0000</guid></item><item><title>即将上任的巴勒斯坦总理在战时经济破坏之际在约旦河西岸组建新内阁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/incoming-palestinian-pm-forms-new-cabinet-in-west-bank-amid-wartime-economic-devastation/0000018e-890f-d782-a7bf-df3f6bb50000</link><description>穆罕默德·穆斯塔法接替穆罕默德·什塔耶，宣布新政府将于周日宣誓就职，并将把加沙重建列为首要议程</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/incoming-palestinian-pm-forms-new-cabinet-in-west-bank-amid-wartime-economic-devastation/0000018e-890f-d782-a7bf-df3f6bb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临的生存问题正走向爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/the-existential-issues-facing-israel-are-heading-towards-explosion/0000018e-8612-d641-abee-cfb78d820000</link><description>经过一年空前的冲突和抗议之后，大多数以色列人认为，纠正基本的司法、民事和安全问题对于国家的生存至关重要。正如内塔尼亚胡政府所希望的那样，让它们继续恶化可能会致命</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:28:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/the-existential-issues-facing-israel-are-heading-towards-explosion/0000018e-8612-d641-abee-cfb78d820000</guid></item><item><title>现代启示录：内塔尼亚胡除了无休止的谎言和脾气之外别无他法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/apocalypse-now-netanyahu-has-nothing-left-to-offer-but-endless-lies-and-temper-tantrums/0000018e-86a8-d9dd-a39f-ceea6d9d0000</link><description>以色列总理本周无法停止撒谎——对美国人、极端正统派和被绑架的以色列人的家人——但他对北方局势的沉默最能说明问题。正统派选民与代表他们的政党之间的关系</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/apocalypse-now-netanyahu-has-nothing-left-to-offer-but-endless-lies-and-temper-tantrums/0000018e-86a8-d9dd-a39f-ceea6d9d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击半年后，10 月 7 日谜题的部分内容仍在拼凑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parts-of-oct-7-puzzle-coming-together-half-year-later/0000018e-869e-d0d3-a98e-d6ffa4d00000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列南部六个月后，很明显，那天发生的极端事件在战前几乎没有被军方排练过</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parts-of-oct-7-puzzle-coming-together-half-year-later/0000018e-869e-d0d3-a98e-d6ffa4d00000</guid></item><item><title>报道：美国悄悄签署向以色列交付价值数十亿美元的战斗机和炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-tells-families-of-kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-he-has-to-make-the-cold-judgment/0000018e-8808-d49b-a3bf-fc1f3ffd0000</link><description>以色列空军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的军事基础设施和火箭发射器 ■ 以色列在叙利亚空袭造成的死亡人数上升至 44 人 ■ 内塔尼亚胡批准代表团前往多哈和开罗继续人质谈判 ■ 以色列国防军称击毙了真主党火箭和导弹副指挥官■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列将加大对真主党的攻击力度 ■ 警察强行驱散耶路撒冷的反战示威；四名抗议者被捕</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 02:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-tells-families-of-kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-he-has-to-make-the-cold-judgment/0000018e-8808-d49b-a3bf-fc1f3ffd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>